title: WWF: Wrestling's Bloopers, Bleeps and Bodyslams (LaserDisc Rip)
description:
Preview: http://i.imgur.com/Dv2mGa2.jpg



This is for all of the old school WWF fans out there.

I found this laserdisc at my local record shop the other day for the grand price of $0.95, snagged it and spent the last two days converting it from LD to digital, in which this torrent contains said digital conversion of the entire laserdisc.

You can probably find VHS rips of this release here and there, but I imagine this is the first LD rip of this inaugural home video release from the WWF (now WWE).

This probably hasn't aged well, but it's a nice time capsule of the long bygone mid 80s period of the World Wrestling entertaining.


Nonetheless, enjoy!
